Introduction

DV.OL was a five-member boy group under DS Entertainment The group is composed of Dokyun, Louis, U, Sungjun, and Sodam, who are all former members of BLANK2Y.

On October 2, 2023, DS Entertainment announced that the five members were preparing for their debut. They have already released a pre-debut digital single called JOURNEY on October 25, 2023. The group had planned to debut in December with their EP album "Dreaming About Our Life", but due to some unforeseen health issues, they have rescheduled their debut to 2024.

On July 2024, Louis announced, through Instagram Live, that the group had unofficially disbanded.
